queries.sql: SELECT departemen.divisi,orders.ID,orders.waktu_end ,mobil.plat_nomor,orders.nama,orders.id_divisi,orders.waktu,orders.tujuan,orders.tujuan_pakai,orders.userid,orders.keterangan,orders.tanggal,pemesanan_mobil.id as id_pemesanan from orders LEFT JOIN pemesanan_mobil on orders.id =pemesanan_mobil.id_pemesanan left join departemen on departemen.id_divisi = orders.id_divisi left join mobil on pemesanan_mobil.id_mobil = mobil.id_mobil WHERE orders.userid = 'Randa_prasetya' and orders.keterangan like '%approve%' ;

SELECT atasan.id_divisi, atasan.userid, departemen.divisi FROM atasan left join user_divisi on atasan.id_divisi = user_divisi.id_divisi left join departemen on atasan.id_divisi = departemen.id_divisi where atasan.userid = 'Randa_prasetya' and user_divisi.userid = 'Randa_prasetya';
